nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A cinematic 8mm analog film portrait of a young woman with dark hair and freckles, captured in a moody, 1950s-inspired color grade—cool blues and muted greens—with visible film grain. She begins by smirking at the camera, then rolls her eyes upward in playful defiance. A delicate wireframe branch with small green berries drifts around her face. As the camera zooms into her mouth, she bites into one berry, teeth and tongue visible in a sensual, slightly surreal close-up. The composition juxtaposes her expressive face with the organic, almost surreal texture of the wire and berries. Shot in a gritty, artful realism style reminiscent of vintage experimental cinema—soft focus, shallow depth, and atmospheric lighting.
